---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<h1 class="text-5xl text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 leading-tight mb-2">üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
	<p class="mb-4">
		Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
		template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
		a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
	</p>
	<p class="mb-4">
		This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
		<code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100 rounded-sm text-base">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
		<a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
		React, or Vue to your project.
	</p>
	<p class="mb-4">Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
	<ul class="mb-4">
		<li>Edit this page in <code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100 rounded-sm text-base">src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
		<li>Edit the site header items in <code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100 rounded-sm text-base">src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
		<li>Add your name to the footer in <code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100 rounded-sm text-base">src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
		<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100 rounded-sm text-base">src/content/blog/</code></li>
		<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100 rounded-sm text-base">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
	</ul>
	<p class="mb-4">
		Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to
		<a href="https://docs.astro.build/" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300">read the docs</a>
		or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
	</p>
	<p class="mb-4">
		Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out
		<a href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300">astro-blog-template</a>
		by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
	</p>
</BaseLayout>
